s conversion hack:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp; <a target="_blank" href="http://github.com/xolox/vim-publish/commit/459b8293a2a85885872603765699a210fe72fb74">http://github.com/xolox/vim-publish/commit/459b8293a2a85885872603765699a210fe72fb74</A><br><br> • Smarter integration with easytags.vim:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp; <a target="_blank" href="http://github.com/xolox/vim-publish/commit/be98f4328bb631cd4c67d8951ff7c413b7cb6355">http://github.com/xolox/vim-publish/commit/be98f4328bb631cd4c67d8951ff7c413b7cb6355</A><br><br> • Fixed easytags#update() to overcome argument limit:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp; <a target="_blank" href="http://github.com/xolox/vim-publish/commit/87b0305bd27d4ee3715790cddc76cc2cfead7c14">http://github.com/xolox/vim-publish/commit/87b0305bd27d4ee3715790cddc76cc2cfead7c14</A></td>
